---
// About section - FULL BLEED image + content
---

<section id="about" class="bg-navy text-white">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2">
    <!-- Left: Image - FULL BLEED -->
    <div class="relative min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[700px]">
      <img 
        src="/images/about-team.png" 
        alt="McCauley Enterprise team" 
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
    
    <!-- Right: Content -->
    <div class="py-16 lg:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 flex items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-gold font-medium mb-4 tracking-wider text-sm uppercase">About Us</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">
          Three Generations.<br/>
          One Standard.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-xl">
          <p>
            McCauley Enterprise was founded in 1978 in Chicago's southwest suburbs with a 
            simple belief: treat every home like it is your own.
          </p>
          <p>
            In 2017, the third generation took the reins, bringing fresh energy while 
            preserving the craftsmanship and integrity that built our reputation. 
            We have grown from a small family operation to a full-service remodeling and 
            construction company — but we have never lost sight of why families trust us.
          </p>
          <p>
            From minor repairs to complete home transformations to commercial build-outs, 
            we bring the same attention to detail and commitment to excellence. 
            Because at the end of the day, our name is on every project.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12 pt-12 border-t border-white/20">
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gold">45+</p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-2">Years in Business</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gold">3rd</p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-2">Generation</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gold">500+</p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-2">Projects</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
